name: The Curse Lifter
description:
Inspired by the film and legend of the cursed village in Spain, this legend tells the story of a village that was hit by a very powerful curse spell and could only be released by a Pope.

The depiction of a very chaotic atmosphere and monsters began to roam and search for prey under the rays of a total solar eclipse that would always shine until a black witch who was in sirius star prophecy came to lift the curse spell from the dead village.

If you like history, movies and stories about witches, dragons, and kingdoms this suits you.
